<title><![CDATA[I’m incredibly grateful for being able to do what I do, and wo...]]></title>
<link>https://imginn.com/p/DExqUjJR6-o/</link>
<guid>https://imginn.com/p/DExqUjJR6-o/</guid>
<description>
<![CDATA[<a href="https://instagram.com/p/DExqUjJR6-o/">View on Instagram</a><p><img src="https://scontent-bos5-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/473660624_18368131453187447_7969770754897324120_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh0.08_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-bos5-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=111&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2AG84iSi2NyGMUionQMA9BI-yEaU3Zv1Wq7yHgCzEVut-CM0pcnXMxDHZMmFQWQ7iFw&_nc_ohc=0X40GTpNH3wQ7kNvgFJAQz8&_nc_gid=f5c6796d6b314386a55672988389db38&edm=AGenrX8BAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AYBLm38_DkBXD_p3zUlHzAGal0b0NAgKV43WmR1qULJQpA&oe=67BE0348&_nc_sid=ed990e" /><br>I’m incredibly grateful for being able to do what I do, and wouldn’t possible without you guys watching my videos, I’m even more grateful for every first responder and person working tirelessly to fight these fires. 🚨👮🏼‍♂️🧑🏼‍🚒It’s not just about handing out burgers or a meal, but about showing up and putting a fucking smile on these heroes’ faces, even if it’s just for a minute. They’re giving everything to protect our community. TO OTHER CONTENT CREATORS AND PEOPLE WITH A FOLLOWING: if you aren’t posting about what’s going on in your communities, and only pushing your content or products.. you should be fucking embarrassed. Step up…. Don’t just sit back and post about meaningless shit. #california #californiafires #palisades #malibu #wildfires #firstresponders #firefighter #firefighters #losangeles #lafires]]>
</description>
<pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 02:25:26 -0500</pubDate>
</item>
